          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed text-pretty">Ganzheitliche Stimmtherapie (ISTP) und Lax Vox® Training zur Wiederherstellung der Balance.</p>
        </div>
  
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-simsek-green/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-simsek-green mb-6">
